Baumer?

822
01:21:56,044 --> 01:21:57,779
Baumer?

823
01:21:59,647 --> 01:22:01,582
Baumer?

824
01:22:06,587 --> 01:22:07,922
Baumer!

825
01:22:10,925 --> 01:22:13,037
<i>Engländer!</i>

826
